settings.description: Ya know, while fire snakes are meant to be reddish orange... they look really good with a cool blue, so... why not build a nice chilly sky level featuring them for one?~
semi-redo of a very old level perhaps. same theme, different layout ya know? though this time I went a bit overboard on them there tilting platforms instead!
just like how the real e-reader levels have a two part special that's all about one tough as nails challenge.. instead of an airship, you get a huge castle! watch out, The Big Boo awaits you!
